2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new deep learning network with constraints as losses to reduce errors. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with supervised learning for joint position and motion estimation. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper deals with kinematic joint estimation which is relevant to robotics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with video human body pose estimation.
